libdkimpp
------------------------------------------
libdkim++ is a lightweight and portable DKIM (RFC4871) library for *NIX,
supporting both signing and DMARC/SDID/ADSP verification, sponsored and used by
Halon Security. libdkim++ has extensive unit test coverage and aims to fully
comply with the current RFC.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.3-1
  libdkim++-devel-2.0.0-1bl2
  libdkim++2-2.0.0-1bl2
  libgcc1-11.4.0-1
  libsodium-devel-1.0.18-1
  libsodium23-1.0.18-1
  libssl-devel-3.0.13-1
  libssl3-3.0.13-1
  libstdc++6-11.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.2.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.42-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-11.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.4.0-1
  libsodium-devel-1.0.18-1
  libssl-devel-3.0.13-1
  ninja-1.12.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/halon/libdkimpp

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/halon/libdkimpp/archive/refs/tags/v2.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libdkimpp-2.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libdkimpp-2.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libdkimpp-2.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libdkimpp-2.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libdkim++2-2.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libdkim++-devel-2.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libdkimpp)
  /usr/bin/dkimtool.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libdkimpp.README
  /usr/share/doc/libdkimpp/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libdkimpp/README.md

(libdkim++2)
  /usr/bin/cygdkim++-2.dll

(libdkim++-devel)
  /usr/include/libdkim++/Base64.hpp
